PrecisAccept, effective on the date of the swearing-in of her successor, the resignation of the HONOURABLE MARGARET NORRIE McCAIN as Lieutenant Governor of the Province of New Brunswick, to which office she was appointed by Commission under the Great Seal of Canada, pursuant to Order in Council P.C. 1994-703 of April 28, 1994.
